{"tid":2293196,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警不展示編號違人權法  官：政府有責任設獨立機制查濫權","createTime":"2020-11-20T05:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T05:45:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a044a4969b9fbe49c44dfcad5518b4830c4ba43","tid":2293196,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/M6NDL4RGERHLXLJ2ZGADRXNIWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FM6NDL4RGERHLXLJ2ZGADRXNIWA%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BeTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=08849cd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FM6NDL4RGERHLXLJ2ZGADRXNIWA%2F&h=930b7bfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/M6NDL4RGERHLXLJ2ZGADRXNIWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警不展示編號違人權法 <br />\n官：政府有責任設獨立機制查濫權<br />\n<br />\n【高院裁決】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高院判決：監警制度無效  梁定邦死撐「老虎冇牙都有爪」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方反修例運動執勤時經常隱藏識別編號，特別是專門應付大型示威的「速龍小隊」，市民根本無從認人無法作出投訴。記協、爆眼教師楊子俊及多名警暴受害者先後向高等法院提司法覆核，挑戰警方做法。法官周家明昨頒下判詞，批評警員在反修例事件執勤時沒有妥善展示獨有編號或標記，做法違反《人權法》，亦指監警會調查權不足，投訴警察課則隸屬警隊管轄，兩者均未能有效處理針對警方的投訴，政府有責任設立獨立機制，調查警方濫權。<br />\n<br />\n記協歡迎法庭裁決，並促請政府及警方盡快回應法庭建議，警務處長亦應立即指示前線警員，執勤時須清楚展示編號，有關當局亦應設獨立調查機制處理市民投訴；警方則指會與律政司研究判詞。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：裁決未定糾正時限 或陷長久戰<br />\n<br />\n本案共涉五宗司法覆核申請，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yHz4Zg1UgVYQF-pIMPxF7Fzl-Co=/2660x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FCBXKRH3MZDKFNSW7VY7NHU5SU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyHz4Zg1UgVYQF-pIMPxF7Fzl-Co%3D%2F2660x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFCBXKRH3MZDKFNSW7VY7NHU5SU.jpg&h=a790d931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■8.31港鐵太子站事件中，速龍小隊並沒有展示任何警員編號或標記。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指行動呼號難識別警身份<br />\n<br />\n周官在判詞引述《人權法》第三條中「任何人不得施以酷刑，或予以殘忍、不人道或侮辱之處遇或懲罰」的部份，表明相關權利是「絕對及不可減損」，即使處於何等嚴重的公眾緊急時刻，該等權利也須受政府尊重及法庭保障。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年1月20日，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n周官指考慮勝訴申請人提出的投訴後，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n為有效行使《人權法》第三條，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警無對違規同袍採取行動<br />\n<br />\n雖然警方要求一般警員及速龍隊員在反修例事件中，分別展示「行動呼號」及「字母數字編號」，惟周官批評此做法難以有效識別警員身份，他解釋指，相關編號非個別警員獨有，例如同一行動呼號會在警員交出後，由同隊同袍「循環再用」，亦有多名警員在相同行動中使用同一呼號，甚至有警員沒展示行動呼號或以其他物件遮蓋。周官並指，沒證據顯示警方曾確保警員妥善展示其編號，及對沒有這樣做的警員採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n周官亦表示，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n判詞形容現行投訴警方的制度為「兩級制」，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，記協亦質疑警方自去年6月12日至提出司法覆核其間，沒有在大型公眾活動上協助傳媒採訪，警方也沒就此跟進。周官指相關部份將另行宣判。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCAL1747、1753、 2671、2703、2915/19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KEsXMrIIkhYFcl0R_NBIb3OwJ1E=/1719x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SEZ6ZETNVBCJFOWE4DABKGO6E4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKEsXMrIIkhYFcl0R_NBIb3OwJ1E%3D%2F1719x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSEZ6ZETNVBCJFOWE4DABKGO6E4.jpg&h=e3fdc0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有警員沒有展示委任證或警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q_pl0ciI_VUGtYiMNBQfSw6cpco=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OZEOJWQEYNHO3PLGIFZMZABPBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ_pl0ciI_VUGtYiMNBQfSw6cpco%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOZEOJWQEYNHO3PLGIFZMZABPBA.jpg&h=995994d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有警員將展示委任證的位置放上其他卡片代替。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6gPzqOVpdFNlU4Dd8Tk5r3FUteI=/1666x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OHKHB7T74FFTBGS5JTPYR4CJHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6gPzqOVpdFNlU4Dd8Tk5r3FUteI%3D%2F1666x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOHKHB7T74FFTBGS5JTPYR4CJHQ.jpg&h=8cf0dcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員會將肩上的號碼隱藏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BSzKttpSljg-l2FlKc1m2ubhcLo=/928x676/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2UY5GTSXBBCBDPLQBQOF5JS47U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBSzKttpSljg-l2FlKc1m2ubhcLo%3D%2F928x676%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2UY5GTSXBBCBDPLQBQOF5JS47U.gif&h=28404450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■部份警員的行動呼號相同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mXOtFrk1bQr06AcNY_hb3yzlwMI=/544x1632/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6KU7J5QYUZBSTC56GMMWJFIZ24.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmXOtFrk1bQr06AcNY_hb3yzlwMI%3D%2F544x1632%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6KU7J5QYUZBSTC56GMMWJFIZ24.gif&h=ff7c0fa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbbb2a6647e820a447ebafe32ae3aa273bda200c","tid":2293196,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:41:12.000Z","msg":"議員犯左國安法要DQ，點解警隊犯左人權法唔洗DQ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2292002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2292002</a><br />\n-分享自LIHKG討論區"},{"pid":"78d9c467e7c2e98057a5a1df0e9952fcc51f8415","tid":2293196,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.g